(3, 5, 'Must visit GOA', 'must-visit-goa', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">This travel guide to\r\nGoa will list out all the practical travel tips to the Coastal state of West\r\nIndia, and the country’s most beloved beach destination. If you are traveling\r\nto Goa for the first time, you will ideally find all the answers related to Goa\r\ntravel in this article! If you do not, ask away in the comments section please!</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"color: rgb(76, 79, 83); font-family: Montserrat, &quot;serif&quot;; font-size: 9.5pt;\">Traveling to Goa is often hailed as a sign of attaining\r\nadolescent in India. Her long stretched coast line promises a new kind of free.\r\nOnce a part of the iconic Hippie trail that flourished all the way from Europe\r\nto Nepal, Goa gave birth to a “New Found Land”, where you can just be, drifting\r\naway from the prejudices and societal niceties that bind you beyond logic can\r\nreason wish!</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Montserrat&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#4C4F53\">You do not visit Goa just once. You want to live there, get\r\ndrunk on the intangible elixir that Arabian Sea serves with salty breeze! Have visited Goa on a long weekend trip from Bangalore. I revisited Goa with another\r\nset of friends, in between a lot of failed Goa trip planning which are an\r\nincumbent part of Indian Millennial’s growing up experience!&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Montserrat&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#4C4F53\">Each time, I visit, Goa opens a new chapter from past, while\r\nsiting glorious nature by side.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6pt; margin-left: 0in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#4C4F53\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Montserrat&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#4C4F53\">Quick &amp; useful Information about Goa travel:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6pt; margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#4C4F53\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Montserrat&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#4C4F53\">Language&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Montserrat&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#4C4F53\">spoken:\r\nKonkoni, Marathi. Largely understood- English and Hindi.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6pt; margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#4C4F53\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Montserrat&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#4C4F53\">Famous&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Montserrat&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#4C4F53\">for\r\nBeautiful beaches, water-sports, night-markets, sea food, yoga, nightlife<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6pt; margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#4C4F53\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Montserrat&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#4C4F53\">Safer&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Montserrat&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#4C4F53\">place\r\nto travel to for solo women in India<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6pt; margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#4C4F53\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Montserrat&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#4C4F53\">It is a tiny state. Prosperous and with higher literacy rate.\r\nOne of the leading tourist destinations in India.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 'You do not visit Goa just once. You want to live there, get drunk on the intangible elixir that Arabian Sea serves with salty breeze!', 'blog-3.jpg', 'Yes', 'MUST VISIT GOA', 'MUST VISIT GOA', '2020-11-19 21:01:33', '2021-12-02 11:50:37'),
(5, 5, 'TOURISM BACK ON TRACK', 'tourism-back-on-track', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#212529\">As of August 2020,\r\nmore countries have reported a success in flattening the curve, and more are on\r\nthe way to reopening their borders, while pockets of the world are slowly\r\nresuming holiday activities, starting domestically.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\nWith the further easing of border restrictions and lockdowns, travel and\r\ntourism leaders and business owners are creating new opportunities through\r\nchange and are pushing new boundaries and strategies to bring the industry back\r\nto life.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\nAs we anticipate more good news from this front, let’s take a look at 6 travel\r\nand tourism trends to expect in a post COVID era, and signs of recovery in the\r\nindustry.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:15.5pt;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#222222\">What are the emerging\r\ntravel trends post-coronavirus?<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#212529\">The trying times has a\r\ndouble meaning in this unprecedented phase. Business may be struggling, but it\r\nhas also open up avenues for them to attempt new things and keep their service\r\nand offering interesting for consumers.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\nRestaurants step up with their takeout menu, hotels throwing staycation\r\npackages and culinary deals, and airlines resorting to creative “flights to\r\nnowhere” like&nbsp;</span><u><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Taiwan’s\r\nEVA Air</span></u><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">,<span style=\"color:#212529\"> to\r\nname a few.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#222222\">1. Staycations and local\r\ntravels<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#212529\">Perhaps one of the\r\nmost significant changes in the local travel scene is the rise in popularity of\r\nstaycations.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\nIn Hong Kong, luxury hotels were fully booked for their staycation offers,\r\nlargely due to the special packages at an affordable price that appeals to the\r\ntravel-starved population. Travellers get a holiday treat while being assured\r\nof the safety from the hotels’ rigorous sanitation processes.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\nThe same phenomenon is also observed at beach and island getaways where private\r\nvillas are snapped up for more intimate, smaller parties.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#222222\">2. Next level takeout<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#212529\">The renewed interest\r\nin domestic holiday locations such as local beaches, hiking trails, camping\r\ngrounds, and parks not only attracted more customers to relevant businesses,\r\nbut it also drew attention to “picnic basket” experiences, where restaurants\r\ncater wicker basket filled with goodies to pleasure-seekers at selected\r\ndestinations.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\nTo stay competitive and relevant, restaurants are coming up with interesting\r\nways to get customers excited about eating from beyond their premises – from\r\nMichelin-starred chefs for private hire, picnic takeout, to cocktail orders\r\nmade fresh upon delivery, and whole high-tea experiences packed up to go.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#222222\">3. Crowd control<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#212529\">One trend that will\r\nlikely gain favour is better crowd management. With many once-bustling tourist\r\ndestinations reduced to minimal activities, people are seeing the positive\r\neffect on the environment and this has given authorities something to consider\r\nin terms of controlling the crowd in the future. This win-win move will help\r\ntourists enjoy a more pleasant visit to popular spots, while also keeping the\r\nenvironment in good shape.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#222222\">4. Travel bubbles<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#212529\">Countries that have\r\nbeen successful in containing the pandemic have demonstrated how tourism can\r\nquickly pick up again. In Baltic States like Estonia, Latvia, and Lithuania,\r\nthey championed the “Travel Bubble”, which is essentially partnerships that\r\nopens their borders and allows their citizens to travel freely within these\r\ncountries without quarantines upon arrival. This free passage is not exclusively\r\nfor tourism, but also to ramp up business activities and save their trade\r\nsectors.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\nThis quarantine-free travel is also opened between&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Austria</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#212529\">&nbsp;and Germany, Switzerland, Liechtenstein,\r\nSlovakia, Czech Republic, and Hungary, and is expected to increase when more\r\ncountries and their neighbours find consensus with their epidemiological\r\nsituation.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#222222\">5. Touch-less travel and\r\nautomation<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#212529\">Touch-less travel – this\r\nis probably the most immediate thing people will prioritise and may also be the\r\nmost visible change in the travel and tourism industry. Even with the strict\r\nhealth and safety protocols, exchanging travel documents in the airport and\r\nhotels still present risk of infection. The same goes for touching surfaces by\r\nthe check-in counter, security checks, border control, as well as hotel front\r\ndesks.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\nThis means automation are expected to become a part of the new normal of travel\r\ntrends in 2021. Biometrics (facial recognition, contactless fingerprint scan,\r\netc.) will replace physical fingerprint and hand scanners.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#222222\">6. Shift to private mode\r\nof transport<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#212529;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">In terms of tourism\r\nproducts, vacation rentals are looking to appeal to the masses in equal if not\r\nmore than hotel bookings due to lesser capacity and greater privacy. The same\r\nis expected with car rentals, as tourists are more likely to shy away from\r\npublic transport like buses and trains.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\nGiven the current situation, travel advisors and travel insurance will also be\r\nin demand for obvious reasons.&nbsp;</span><br></p>', 'POST COVID TOURISM BACK ON TRACK', 'blog-5.jpg', 'Yes', 'TOURSIM BACK ON TRACK', 'TOURSIM BACK ON TRACK', '2020-11-19 21:56:00', '2021-12-02 11:26:26'),
(6, 4, 'CAMP AT WADI RUM', 'camp-at-wadi-rum', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Camping Overnight</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Everyone should\r\ncamp overnight in the desert wadi. It’s a fantastic experience and\r\ninexpensive.&nbsp;The camping grounds are scattered around the valley but are\r\ninconspicuous and low profile.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">A word of\r\nwarning: unscrupulous tour operators that don’t have a licence to lead groups\r\nin Wadi Rum often trick visitors into camping outside of the&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\r\nnone windowtext 0in;padding:0in\">UNESCO World Heritage area</span></strong>. I\r\nhaven’t seen these areas, and by all accounts, they are beautiful places to\r\nstay. But if you’re here to visit the real Wadi Rum, make sure you stay with a\r\nreputable guide. The GPS on your phone will also show you if you’ve strayed too\r\nfar off track.&nbsp;</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Most of the camps\r\nwill provide food in the form of a&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;\r\nmso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in\">traditional underground bbq</span></strong>,\r\ncalled a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/travel/story/20180903-zarb-the-bedouin-answer-to-barbecue\" target=\"_blank\"><em><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: windowtext; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">zarb</span></em></a>. That’s the food that goes underground, not you.\r\nYour evening’s entertainment will be traditional Bedouin songs, played by\r\nmusicians who also double as cooks, guides, and most likely, your driver for\r\nthe Wadi Rum tours.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.5pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">The\r\ntents range from square framed shacks with material stitched onto the outside\r\nto luxury tents&nbsp;good enough for the likes of Elon Musk.</span><br></p>', 'Camping a night in WADI-RUM is next level of experience while travelling in JORDAN', 'blog-6.jpg', 'Yes', 'CAMP AT WADI RUM', 'CAMP AT WADI RUM', '2020-11-19 21:57:33', '2021-12-02 11:39:57'),
(7, 3, 'FAMILY IN PANDEMIC', 'family-in-pandemic', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Family talk: Respondents also described feeling a\r\nheightened sense of loneliness when they heard others talk about their\r\nfamilies, how much they missed them and how frequently they were keeping in contact.\r\nThe focus in the media on families connecting and supporting each other also\r\nadded to these feelings, with some respondents comparing this to the sense\r\nof&nbsp;isolation they felt at festival&nbsp; time.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">I feel the isolation of family estrangement more keenly. I\r\nam very aware of friends and others talking about Zoom calls with their\r\nfamilies. There is always coverage on the news etc. about what families would\r\nusually be doing, and the compromises they are all making, and the painfulness\r\nof&nbsp;my situation is heightened. Everyone is now focusing on their support\r\nnetworks more than ever, including family – it is painful to hear about other\r\npeople’s parents and wider family networks, when you don’t have a similar\r\nnetwork to belong to. Every single advert is also enforcing over and over again\r\nthe message of family being the most important thing, much like Christmas. I’m\r\nfeeling much of the same loneliness I do every December, perhaps more\r\nexacerbated by the additional stress of the situation, and the enforced social\r\nisolation</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">Worry about family. Some felt more isolated during the\r\ncrisis because they were worried about their estranged family member(s) but\r\nwere not able to find out how they were.</span></p>', 'Worry about family. Some felt more isolated during the crisis because they were worried about their estranged family member(s) but were not able to find out how they were.', 'blog-7.jpg', 'Yes', 'FAMILY IN PANDEMIC', 'FAMILY IN PANDEMIC', '2020-11-28 00:13:12', '2021-12-02 12:00:33'),
(8, 1, 'GREEN EARTH', 'green-earth', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#2E2E2E\">As the transmission of corona virus (COVID-19)\r\nincreases rapidly, the whole world adopted the curfew/lockdown activity with\r\nrestriction of human mobility. The imposition of quarantine stopped all the\r\ncommercial activity that greatly affects the various important environmental\r\nparameters which directly connected to human health. As all the types of\r\nsocial, economic, industrial and urbanization activity suddenly shut off,\r\nnature takes the advantages and showed improvement in the quality of air,\r\ncleaner rivers, less noise pollution, undisturbed and calm wildlife. This\r\nresearch aims to discuss the COVID-19 effect on the global environment. The\r\noutcome of this research says that “</span><em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi\">Although coronavirus vaccine is not available\r\ncoronavirus itself is earth\'s vaccine and us humans are the virus</span></em>”.</p>', 'COVID-19 became the opportunity for the earth to build a clear blue sky and clean the air. During the period of lockdown across the world, the sight of the blue sky created a sense of optimism among the people towards a clean and better environment', 'blog-8.jpg', 'Yes', 'GREEN EARTH', 'GREEN EARTH', '2020-11-28 00:13:49', '2021-12-02 12:10:37'),
(9, 1, 'COMFORT HOUSING', 'comfort-housing', '<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin\">If you are going to be looking for an apartment to move into soon\r\nand you haven’t yet decided on the type of apartment you want, you might find\r\nyourself wondering if a luxury apartment is something you want to go for. In\r\norder to determine whether you should go with a<span style=\"border:none windowtext 1.0pt;\r\nmso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%;\">&nbsp;</span>luxury apartment</span>, you\r\ncan ask yourself the four questions listed below. The way you answer these\r\nquestions can help you to decide whether a regular apartment or a luxury\r\napartment is best for your needs.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;\r\npadding:0in\">Can you afford a luxury apartment?</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin\">Since an apartment is a place you will likely rent until you are\r\nready to purchase a home at some point in the future, you want to make sure you\r\nare spending a reasonable percentage of your income on housing. If you can\r\nswing a luxury apartment, then it can be a home you can be comfortable and\r\nproud in until you are ready to become a homeowner. If you are able to swing a\r\nluxury apartment, then you will enjoy living in an amazing home while you\r\nrent.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;\r\npadding:0in\">Will you be spending a good amount of time at home?</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin\">You may not feel such a need to have a luxurious apartment if you\r\nspend most of your time at work and out with friends and family. However, if\r\nyou have some downtime during the week, then you want to spoil yourself when\r\nyou get the chance. Being able to spoil yourself just by spending time in your\r\nown home can be great, and this is what a luxury apartment can offer you — the\r\nperfect home environment to treat yourself like royalty.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;\r\npadding:0in\">Would you appreciate all the amenities you would be afforded?</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin\">A big part of what luxury apartments have to offer is access to\r\nmany great amenities not only in the apartment but also outside of it. While\r\neach luxury apartment complex can differ, there are some things many of them do\r\noffer their residents. A few examples of such amenities include large sparkling\r\npools, tennis courts, a fitness center, coffee bars, an onsite masseur, on-site\r\npilates or yoga classes, and a business center.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;\r\npadding:0in\">Are you ready to be completely spoiled?</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin\">If you love the idea of spoiling yourself, then a luxury apartment\r\nis for you. From the state-of-the-art smart appliances to a fantastic home\r\ntheater system, when you walk in your luxury apartment, you will feel it caters\r\nto all your needs.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>', 'Are you ready to be completely spoiled?\r\nIf you love the idea of spoiling yourself, then a luxury apartment is for you. From the state-of-the-art smart appliances to a fantastic home theater system, when you walk in your luxury apartment, you will feel it caters to all your needs.', 'blog-9.jpg', 'Yes', 'COMFORT HOUSING', 'COMFORT HOUSING', '2020-11-28 00:14:30', '2021-12-02 12:19:21');

