(2, 7, 'NEPAL - MYSTIC', 'Mystic-Nepal', 'destination-61ba9f4ea84fa.jpg', 'About Nepal', 'Nepal is a landlocked country, it is not near to ocean, but surrounded by China (on North) & India (on South). Mt. Everest the highest mountain on earth it’s shared with China on the Northern border. Nepal has one of the largest and most varied populations of birds in the world. Nepal is home to literally tens-of-thousands of religious areas central to not only Buddhism and Hinduism,  but to numerous lesser-known traditions. This extensive and ancient cultural environment lends itself to rich anthropological tours; art tours and even a specific tour just to meet Nepalese shamans who gather at a remote lake deep in a remote Himalayan valley.', 'Nepal Programs', 'Nepal', 'Nepal', 'Nepal', NULL, '<br>', '<br>', '<div><br></div>', '<br>', '<br>', 0, 'Nepal', 'Nepal', '2021-05-27 04:17:29', '2022-01-12 04:22:50'),
(3, 7, 'TIBET - POTALA', 'Tibet-potala', 'destination-3.jpg', 'About TIBET', 'Tibet Autonomous Region includes visits to some of the most important highlights on this unique high altitude plateau.  Tibet lies at the center of Asia, with an area of 2.5 million square kilometers. Encircled by the Earth’s highest mountains, Tibet is a vast, arid plateau with an average altitude of 14,000 feet above sea level. The Tibetan plateau has unique and exceptional ecosystems. The headwaters of Asia’s major rivers originate on the Tibetan plateau, which supply 85% of the population of Asia with water—approximately 47% of the world’s population.', 'Our Tibet Packages', 'Tibet', 'Tibet', 'Tibet', '<span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">Coming Soon...</span><br>', '<span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">Coming Soon...</span><br>', '<span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">Coming Soon...</span><br>', '<span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">Coming Soon...</span><br>', '<span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">Coming Soon...</span><br>', '<span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">Coming Soon...</span><br>', 0, 'Tibet', 'Tibet', '2021-05-27 04:18:58', '2021-12-15 04:46:16'),
(4, 8, 'INDIA - TAJ MAHAL', 'India', 'destination-4.jpg', 'About India', 'India is a large country located on the Indian subcontinent in south-central Asia. India is geographically positioned both in the Northern and Eastern hemispheres of the Earth. It is bordered by Afghanistan and Pakistan in the north-west; by China, Nepal and Bhutan in the north; and by Bangladesh and Burma (Myanmar) in the east.\r\nIndia is a pictorial kaleidoscope of landscapes, opulent historical sites and royal cities, golden beaches, misty mountain retreats, colorful people, rich cultures and festivities.\r\nIndia is rapidly gaining ground in the international scenario as a popular destination for foreign travellers, international students, and even for some others who choose to migrate to this mystical land for health and medical tourism. A trip to India is exceptional for tourists, as this wonderland has always been a prime travel destination for those who are charmed by exotic beaches of the south India, the mesmerising backwaters, the spell-binding remains of the ancient civilization in the north, the lofty mountain ranges along the Ghats, lush greenery, the tropical rain forests etc.\r\n\r\nIt is said that if you have travelled the world then you have seen half the world, and if you have visited only the Indian subcontinent, you have seen the whole world! India has metamorphosis into one of the most sought after destinations for travel, much due to the presence of several renowned world heritage sites, and an inherent spiritualistic force, which pulls enthusiastic travelers towards it from all over the world.', 'Tour Packages', 'India', 'India', 'India', 'Coming Soon...', '<span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">Coming Soon...</span><br>', '<span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">Coming Soon...</span><br>', '<span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">Coming Soon...</span><br>', '<span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">Coming Soon...</span><br>', '<span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">Coming Soon...</span><br>', 0, 'Taj Mahal-India', 'Taj Mahal-India', '2021-05-27 04:23:02', '2022-01-12 04:23:17'),
(7, 10, 'BHUTAN - The Last Shangri-La', 'The-Last-Shangri-La', 'destination-61b5e941c9457.jpg', 'The Last Shangri-La', 'Bhutan\'s tourism sector is regarded as one of the most exclusive travel destinations in the world. Bhutan is just about size of Switzerland bounded on north by Tibet, and nudging its remaining borders with India. Virtually the entire country is mountainous, peaking at 7554m (24,777ft). North to south it features three geographic regions; the high Himalayas of the north, the hills and valleys of the centre, and the foothills and plains of the south.', 'The Last Shangri-La', 'The Last Shangri-La', 'The Last Shangri-La', 'The Last Shangri-La', '<br>', '<br>', '<br>', '<br>', '<br>', '<br>', 0, 'The Last Shangri-La', 'The Last Shangri-La', '2021-05-27 04:28:48', '2021-12-15 04:48:18'),
(10, 1, 'JORDAN - PETRA', 'Jordan-petra', 'destination-619f2987cebae.jpg', 'About Jordan', 'Jordan – Destination in Holy Land Tours\r\nA tour of the holy land isn’t complete without visiting Jordan. See the Great Hashemite Kingdom of Jordan and its capitol city, Amman. You’ll see Bethany, Jerash and Petra. Bethany is where Jesus was identified by John the Baptist, where Elijah and Elisha crossed the Jordan and the area where the children of Jerusalem, led by Joshua entered the Promised Land. Petra is a must see destination in terms of history, religious significance and spirituality. This Christianity centered, holy land tour is sure to refresh your body and soul and let you feel the historical significance of the location.', 'OUR CLASSIC TOURS - JORDAN', 'JORDAN - Combined Tours', 'JORDAN - Combined Tours', 'JORDAN - Combined Tours', '<div><br></div>', '<br>', '<span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">Coming Soon...</span><br>', '<span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">Coming Soon...</span><br>', '<span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">Coming Soon...</span><br>', '<span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">Coming Soon...</span><br>', 0, 'JORDAN - Combined Tours', 'JORDAN - Combined Tours', '2021-10-27 07:21:24', '2022-01-12 04:16:54'),
(11, 5, 'EGYPT - PYRAMIDS', 'Egypt', 'destination-61a857537b387.jpg', 'Egypt', 'Egypt, is also a linking country with Middle East & northeast Africa, dates to the time of the pharaohs. Millennia-old monuments sit along the fertile Nile River Valley, including Giza\'s colossal Pyramids and Great Sphinx as well as Luxor\'s hieroglyph-lined Karnak Temple and Valley of the Kings tombs. Great Ottoman landmarks like Muhammad Ali Mosque, Egyptian Museum, and a trove of antiquities is the home to its capital CAIRO.', 'Egypt Tours', 'Egypt Tours', 'Egypt Tours', 'Egypt Tours', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">coming Soon...</span><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">coming Soon...</span><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">coming Soon...</span><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">coming Soon...</span><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">coming Soon...</span><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">coming Soon...</span><br></p>', 0, 'Egypt Tours', 'Egypt Tours', '2021-10-27 09:58:10', '2021-12-02 05:19:15'),
(12, 6, 'DUBAI - LUXURY', 'Dubai-luxury', 'destination-61d1917200cf2.jpg', 'Dubai', 'Dubai is a city known for luxury shopping, ultramodern architecture and a lively nightlife scene. BURJ KHALIFA 830 meters-tall tower, a dominating skyscraper-filled skyline and the base has Water Fountain with jets & lights choreographed to music. \r\nArtificial islands offshore, The Palm, a resort with water and marine-animal park, tree-shaped Palm Jumeirah island is known for glitzy hotels, posh apartment towers and upmarket global restaurants.\r\nBURJ AL ARAB Jumeirah is designed like a billowing sail standing height of 321 m. One of the most consistently voted the world’s most luxurious hotel, round-the-clock private butlers and unique transfers of Rolls-Royce fleet with private beach. It has 199 luxury suites range from 170 to 780 square meters having rain shower also a Jacuzzi in every suite, it also has a range of award winning restaurants, conference hall with magnificent banqueting venues.', 'Dubai Tours', 'Dubai Tours', 'Dubai Tours', 'Dubai Tours', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">BURJ AL ARAB Jumeirah is designed like a billowing sail standing height of 321 m. One of the most consistently voted the world’s most luxurious hotel, round-the-clock private butlers and unique transfers of Rolls-Royce fleet with private beach. It has 199 luxury suites range from 170 to 780 square meters having rain shower also a Jacuzzi in every suite, it also has a range of award winning restaurants, conference hall with magnificent banqueting venues.</span><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">coming Soon...</span><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">coming Soon...</span><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">coming Soon...</span><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">coming Soon...</span><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">coming Soon...</span><br></p>', 0, 'Dubai Tours', 'Dubai Tours', '2021-10-27 10:02:36', '2022-01-02 11:50:10'),
(13, 1, 'JERUSALEM - HOLY LAND', 'holy-land', 'destination-617a8a164ec98.jpg', 'About Holy Land', 'Jordan – Destination in Holy Land Tours\r\nA tour of the holy land isn’t complete without visiting Jordan. See the Great Hashemite Kingdom of Jordan and its capitol city, Amman. You’ll see Bethany, Jerash and Petra. Bethany is where Jesus was identified by John the Baptist, where Elijah and Elisha crossed the Jordan and the area where the children of Jerusalem, led by Joshua entered the Promised Land. Petra is a must see destination in terms of history, religious significance and spirituality. This Christianity centered, holy land tour is sure to refresh your body and soul and let you feel the historical significance of the location.', 'Holy Land Tour Packages', 'Holy Land Tours', 'Holy Land Tours', 'Holy Land Tours', '<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">A\r\nwonderful tour to some of the world’s holy destinations where Jesus Christ was\r\nborn or where the foundations of Christianity originated will surely fulfill\r\nyour spiritual curiosities and desires. Planning and joining us on one of our\r\nholy land tours is certainly the way to purify you and will relax your spirit.\r\nIf you’ve ever wanted to visit the birthplace of your faith and are planning on\r\nbooking a trip to the holy land</span><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">Coming Soon...</span><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">Coming Soon...</span><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">Coming Soon...</span><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">Coming Soon...</span><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(111, 111, 111);\">Coming Soon...</span><br></p>', 0, 'Holy Land', 'Holy Land', '2021-10-28 06:35:14', '2022-01-12 04:18:39'),
(14, 3, 'JORDAN - DEAD SEA', 'dead-sea', 'destination-619dcdfe56d76.jpg', 'Dead Sea', 'The sunset touching distant hills with ribbons of fire across the waters of the Dead Sea brings a sense of unreality to culminate a day’s visit to the lowest point on earth, some 400 meters below sea level. To reach this unique spot the visitor enjoys a short, 55 kilometer drive from Amman, surrounded by a landscape which could be from another planet. En route a stone marker indicates “Sea Level”, but the Dead Sea itself is not reached before descending another 400 meters below this sign. As the name suggests, the sea is devoid of life due to an extremely high content of salts and minerals. But it is these natural elements which give the waters their curative powers, recognized since the 2,000 years ago. They also provide the raw materials for the renowned Jordanian Dead Sea Bath Salts and cosmetic products which are marketed world wide. The Dead Sea is normally as calm as a mill pond, with barely a ripple disturbing its surface, but it can become turbulent. During most days, however, the water shimmers under a beating sun. where rocks meet its lapping edges, they become snow like, covered with a thick, gleaming white deposit that gives the area a strange, surreal sense like that of another world. Because of its extremely high content of salt and other minerals, the Dead Sea is devoid of plant and animal life. The tourist facilities provide accommodations for changing into swimming attire so the visitor can wade into the warm, soothing water. Try as one may, it is impossible to sink in the thick brine which is four times as salty as regular sea water.', 'Our Dead Sea Tour Packages', 'Dead Sea', 'Dead Sea', 'Dead Sea', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'Dead Sea-Jordan', 'Dead Sea', '2021-11-11 04:17:48', '2022-01-12 04:19:25'),
(16, 11, 'MT. KAILASH - Heaven on Earth', 'MT.-KAILASH', 'destination-61b967024087d.jpg', 'About Mt. Kailash', 'MT. KAILASH is also known as the NAVAL center of the Earth, the literal meaning of MOUNT KAILASH is Precious jewel of the eternal show, lying in the Tibetan range, this mountain is at the axis of the earth and is devoted to Adi Yogi Shiva and his eternal spirit mate Shakti. It is also the main source of the rivers Indus, Sutlej, Brahmaputra and Karnali and is considered to be the most sacred mountain.', 'MT. KAILASH PACKAGE', 'MT. KAILASH TOUR', 'MT. KAILASH TOUR', 'MT. KAILASH TOUR', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'MT. KAILASH TOUR', 'MT KAILASH', '2021-12-13 13:22:42', '2021-12-19 04:11:06'),
(17, 0, 'CANADA - AWE', 'CANADA-AWE', 'destination-61bb1c32a12ce.jpg', 'About Canada', 'Canada is a country that has much to offer visitors, from island sights to scenic mountain waterfalls. Stretching from the Atlantic to the Pacific coasts, this former French and British colony has a rich heritage from the North Coast Indians of British Columbia to the French explorers of Quebec. Since both French and English are the national languages, a visit to Canada is like visiting two countries. Indeed, Canada has appeal for travelers who are interested in nature and cosmopolitan cities. \r\nVisit Canada in 10 days is a perfect combination of beautiful landscapes and popular cities of the region, visiting Vancouver & Calgary, famous Jasper including the Banff National Parks.', 'TOUR PACKAGE - CANADA', 'TOUR PACKAGE - CANADA', 'AWE CANADA', 'AWE CANADA', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'Canada', 'Canada', '2021-12-16 05:20:24', '2022-01-12 04:13:56'),
(18, 12, 'JORDAN - OPTIONAL TRIPS', 'OPTIONAL-TOURS---JORDAN', 'destination-61c54b850254d.jpg', 'About Jordan', 'IN & AROUND Tours of JORDAN', 'OPTIONAL TOURS - JORDAN', 'OPTIONAL TOURS - JORDAN', 'OPTIONAL TOURS - JORDAN', 'OPTIONAL TOURS - JORDAN', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'OPTIONAL TOURS - JORDAN', 'OPTIONAL TOURS - JORDAN', '2021-12-24 04:24:37', '2022-01-12 04:26:29');

