(11, 1, 'Paragliding above Pokhara (US$.80)', 'Paragliding-above-Pokhara-(US$.80)', 'package-main-photo-6164ec8a4af0e.jpg', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">How safe is Pokhara’s Paragliding?</span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Paragliding in\r\nPokhara is safer since the internationally certificated pilots are only allowed\r\nto fly in the sky. Pilots are much more experienced, and they take care of your\r\nsafety and comfort. You can be carefree and enjoy the majestic views of\r\nPokhara.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit\" id=\"How_to_book_Paragliding_in_Pokhara\">How to book Paragliding in Pokhara?</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">You can book a\r\nflight at least a day ahead. In advance booking, you can book by phone, email,\r\nor a person over there. You are required to deposit Rs. 1000-2000 for the\r\nconfirmation.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit\" id=\"Is_there_an_age_limit_for_Pokhara_Paragliding\">Is there an age limit for\r\nPokhara Paragliding?</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Almost there is\r\nno age limit for paragliding, but it is useful if you avoid bringing small\r\nbabies on the flight.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 'Paragliding can be both a recreational and competitive flying sport. A paraglider is a free-flying, foot launched glider aircraft. The pilot sits in a harness suspended below a fabric wing, whose shape is formed by its suspension lines and the pressure of air entering vents in the front of the wing. Despite not having an engine, […]', '28.2096,83.9856', '1', 'APR OCT NOV', 'Adventurous', '23rd November 2022', '2021/10/01', '2021/10/01', '2021/10/09', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d210147.39707064038!2d-58.573384362124045!3d-34.61546111822767!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x95bcca3b4ef90cbd%3A0xa0b3812e88e88e87!2sBuenos+Aires%2C+Argentina!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sbd!4v1544189305968\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Intro&nbsp;</span></u></b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; text-align: justify;\">The main area for paragliding is Sarangkot in the Pokhara\r\nvalley, a site which offers spectacular views of three 8,000m peaks and\r\nfriendly and constant conditions for paragliding throughout the year.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><b><u>Tandem Flights<o:p></o:p></u></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\">Tandem\r\nflight involves flying along with an instructor&nbsp; as a passenger. Both the\r\npilot and passenger have separate harnesses, which feels like an armchair. Once\r\nafter take off the passenger sits back and enjoys the magic of being airborne.\r\nNothing can beat the thrill of flying&nbsp; alongside eagles and vultures to\r\nguide us all the while enjoying stunning views of the Annapurna range, pristine\r\nlakes and verdant valleys like nowhere else on earth.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\">&nbsp;</span><b><u><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Cloud\r\nBuster</span></u></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">This mid\r\nday flight gives you the thrill of flying in rising currents of warm air in\r\norder to stay aloft in the air, and soar all the way up to clouds accompanied\r\nby eagles and vultures. And we come to land by one of the bars very close to\r\nLakeside.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: left;\">Time: Approx 20 – 30 minute flight</span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">\r\nCOST US$.80 <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Cross\r\nCountry</span></u></b><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">We take you on an unforgettable\r\njourney towards the north of Sarangkot ridge overlooking an amazing backdrop of\r\nthe Annapurnas while silently gliding over villages forgotten by time. We aim\r\nto fly as far as possible using thermals to our advantage and return to land by\r\nLakeside the same afternoon.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Time: Approx 50 – 60 minute flight:<br>\r\nCOST US$.120<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 80, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#595959;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;\r\npadding:0in\">Privacy policy</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#29293A\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#595959;\r\nborder:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in\">Any\r\npersonal information that we collect about you may be used for any purpose\r\nassociated with the operation of a Trip or to send you marketing material in\r\nrelation to our events and special offers. We will otherwise treat your details\r\nin accordance with our privacy policy (available for viewing on our Website).</span><span style=\"font-size:5.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><