ous barbeque buffet. Adding to the atmosphere of the night is an enchanting belly dancer performing to the Arabic rhythms.</p><p><br></p><p>DAY 2: DEPARTURE</p><p>Check out before noon and transfer to Dubai International Airport</p>', 85, '<p>Dubai Stop Over (2 days)<br></p>', '<p>Dubai Stop Over (2 days)<br></p>', 'Yes', '12', 9, 'Dubai Stop Over (2 days)', 'Dubai Stop Over (2 days)', '2021-10-27 11:48:08', '2021-11-07 09:19:12');
