is is the place where Herod had ordered\r\nthe incarceration of St. John the Baptist after the fateful dance of Salome.\r\nBack to your hotel in Dead Sea<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 890, '<p><br></p>', '<p><br></p>', 'No', '14', 1, 'Time to float in dead sea', 'Time to float in dead sea', '2021-11-12 04:47:21', '2021-12-06 13:18:03'),
