\"><span lang=\"NL-BE\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Amman</span></a><span lang=\"NL-BE\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">,&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jordan\" title=\"Jordan\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span lang=\"NL-BE\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Jordan</span></a><span lang=\"NL-BE\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;was built between 1982\r\nand 1989. </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">It is capped by a magnificent\r\nblue mosaic dome beneath which 3,000 Muslims may offer prayer. Then start the\r\nAmman City Tour of the downtown in Amman and visit the Citadel, see the Temple\r\nof Hercules, the Umayyad Palace, Byzantine Church and the Amman Archeological\r\nMuseum. Exhibited here are statues dating back to 6,000 B.C and the Dead Sea\r\nBronze Scroll. Close by is a Roman Theatre which holds the Museum of Popular\r\nTraditions and The Folklore Museum. Drive through the old Downtown area of\r\nAmman, and then we return you to the hotel.<b><span style=\"background:yellow;\r\nmso-highlight:yellow\"> Overnight: Amman Hotel</span></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0in;text-align:justify\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#006CAA;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;\r\npadding:0in\">Day 14:</span></u></b><b><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Amman\r\nHotel – Amman airport for flight departure</span></u></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0in;text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#333333\">Depending on your flight (latest\r\ncheck out at 12 PM); our driver will pick you up for a direct transfer to Queen\r\nAlia International Airport for your departure flight.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 1300,