/span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#29293A\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>', '<p><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Calibri, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Program includes:</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\">Meet and assist at Queen Alia Airport upon arrival and departure.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\">4 nights’ accommodation includes bed and breakfast sharing twin&nbsp;or triple standard room. (Single supplement applies if you want a single room).<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\">Entrance fees to the mentioned sites in the program. 2 hours jeep tour in Wadi Rum.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\">Transport by experienced English speaking driver in air-conditioned vehicle.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\">English speaking local guide in Petra for 3 – 2 hours for individuals (4 -1) persons.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\">Government Licensed malty speaking tour guide on days of sightseeing from&nbsp;groups 5 persons and more.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\">Jordan collective visa for groups 5 persons and more (full passport details must&nbsp;received prior arrival).<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\">Porterage at hotels and airport.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Calibri, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Calibri, &quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Program excludes:</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\">All lunches and dinner (please see meals supplement below).<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\">All drinks.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\">Any services not mentioned in the program.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\">Visa fee to Jordan ($USD 60.00) per person for individuals (4 – 1) persons.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\">Departure taxes (15$ pp at land borders). Airport tax is usually included on air-tickets. Taxes subject to change with no notice.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\">Tips for driver, guide and hotel staff.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\">Any airfare.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><p></p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(111, 111, 111); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: black; font-