INSERT INTO `page_privacy_items` (`id`, `name`, `detail`, `status`, `seo_title`, `seo_meta_description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(1, 'Privacy Policy', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 2.75pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;robotoblack&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#595959;text-transform:uppercase;\r\nletter-spacing:.35pt;mso-font-kerning:18.0pt\">PRIVACY POLICY<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16.35pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;robotoregular&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#595959\">GO2Tourism is committed to protecting your Personal Information\r\nthat you share with us. We want you to understand our Privacy Policy and what\r\nit means to you, our customer. Please take a moment to review this Privacy\r\nPolicy. By using our website or the services offered by us, you are consenting\r\nto our use of such personal information as you provide to us as described\r\nherein. If you do not consent to our use of your information, please do not use\r\nour services. Any questions you have about our Privacy Policy, or the\r\ninformation contained herein can be directed to our Privacy Officer\r\nat:&nbsp;info@go2tourism.com.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16.35pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;robotoregular&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#595959\">We do our utmost to ensure your personal information is\r\nsafeguarded and protected.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 10.9pt 0in 8.2pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;robotobold&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#595959\">What is\r\nconsidered personal information and why would it be collected?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16.35pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;robotoregular&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#595959\">GO2Tourism collects personal information only to the extent\r\nnecessary to deliver the services, products, or information you, or an agent or\r\nother passenger bookings on your behalf, request.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16.35pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;robotoregular&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#595959\">GO2Tourism, either directly or through our agency and booking\r\npartners collects, holds, uses and discloses, only as necessary the following\r\npersonal information from customers and others in the course of offering\r\nservices or providing services to you: full name, age, home address, phone\r\nnumber, e-mail address, passport and travel medical information, where\r\nrequired, insurance details, ISIC information, where applicable, nationality,\r\nresidency, nutrition preferences, trip evaluations, travel &amp; accommodation\r\npreferences, comments you provide us, trip destination information, credit card\r\nand/or other payment information, etc. The collection of this information is\r\ndone to allow us to provide services to you as requested.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16.35pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;robotoregular&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#595959\">We may also collect personal information, including contact\r\ninformation, if you subscribe to our newsletter, or to request a brochure, which\r\nwe will use only to provide you with the service you have requested (or other\r\nsubstantially similar services directly related to your request).<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16.35pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;robotoregular&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#595959\">GO2Tourism collects personal information from those individuals\r\napplying for employment or similar positions with the company to the extent\r\nnecessary to (i) identify the individual and (ii) evaluate their suitability\r\nfor the position applied for. This information may include name, contact\r\ninformation, educational and employment background, criminal record information,\r\nresidency and/or citizenship information, and other information necessary for\r\nus to screen potential employees and staff.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16.35pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;robotoregular&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#595959\">GO2Tourism collects personal information from agents and\r\nagencies to the extent required to allow agents to book GO2Tourism trips, and\r\nto be properly credited for such booking, as necessary and as dictated by the\r\nrelationship between the agent and GO2Tourism. Such information may include\r\nname, employment relationship or employer information, work or business\r\naddress, etc.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 10.9pt 0in 8.2pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;robotobold&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#595959\">How is\r\nmy personal information used or disclosed?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16.35pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;robotoregular&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#595959\">GO2Tourism uses this personal information to provide the\r\nservices and/or products you have requested, or to provide you with information\r\nabout those services or GO2Tourism. This includes using personal information\r\nto: register you to receive newsletters, answer your request for further\r\ninformation about our trips, make a booking or booking(s), provide you with\r\ninformation about the Company and/or our services, and to receive and implement\r\nfeedback on those services. Furthermore, the personal information allows us to:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 1.1pt 0in 5.45pt 10.9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n9.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nSymbol;color:#595959\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;robotoregular&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#595959\">Understand your needs as a customer and determine eligibility\r\nfor our products and services.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 1.1pt 0in 5.45pt 10.9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n9.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nSymbol;color:#595959\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;robotoregular&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#595959\">Inform you about our products and services, or those of our\r\npartners that we believe may be of interest to you.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 1.1pt 0in 5.45pt 10.9pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; 